Titolo: Konung: Legends of the North

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Konung: Legend of the North is a role-playing video game (CRPG) developed by 1C and released in 2000 by Strategy First.  The game takes place in the 7th century in Scandinavia, a world full of legends and myths. The main character looks for three pieces of an amulet to open a gate that leads to a mighty dragon, who defends the "Bracelet of Dominion". The game has 2 sequels, Konung 2: Blood of Titans. and Konung III: Ties of the Dynasty.